Message.En: Ordinary Power Is No Match for Them
Message.Jp: 並の戦力では敵わない

Message.En:
I thought maybe there was something I could do,
so I came all the way here—but—
I was attacked by <LQVA> <LQEM> 
and barely made it back!
Elite members, please be careful!
Message.Jp:
俺にも何かできることはないかなって
ここまで来てみたけど――
<LQVA>匹の<LQEM>にやられて、帰るのがやっとの有様だ！
精鋭の皆さん、気を付けてくれよ！
